<p>The Problem: <strong>Conditional</strong> obedience to God</p>

<h3 id="god-wants-your-heart">God Wants Your Heart</h3>

<ol>
  <li>God wasn‚Äôt trying to <strong>punish</strong> His people.</li>
  <li>God was trying to <strong>restore</strong> His people.</li>
  <li>The greatest evidence of a right heart for God is <strong>obedience</strong> to God.</li>
</ol>

<p><em>‚ÄúSin is like spaghetti sauce; it stains everything it touches.‚Äù</em></p>

<p><em>‚ÄúWe don‚Äôt obey so God will bless us. We obey because we love Him.‚Äù</em></p>

